{"aid": "igkpukadak42eq", "error": null, "result": {"default_anonymity": "no", "status": "active", "i_edits": [], "q_edits": [], "bookmarked": 4, "request_instructor": 0, "history": [{"uid": "i6roqnlkmtw", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-05-07T07:17:45Z", "content": "<p>lab7里面为每个mm_struct增加了一个信号量</p>\n<pre>struct mm_struct {\n    list_entry_t mmap_list;        // linear list link which sorted by start addr of vma\n    struct vma_struct *mmap_cache; // current accessed vma, used for speed purpose\n    pde_t *pgdir;                  // the PDT of these vma\n    int map_count;                 // the count of these vma\n    void *sm_priv;                 // the private data for swap manager\n    int mm_count;                  // the number ofprocess which shared the mm\n    semaphore_t mm_sem;            // mutex for using dup_mmap fun to duplicat the mm \n    int locked_by;                 // the lock owner process&#39;s pid\n};</pre>\n<p>然后有两个操作lock_mm和unlock_mm可以用来保证同一时间只有一个进程能够访问某个mm_struct</p>\n<p>我查到的唯一一个用到lock_mm的地方是在</p>\n<p>process/proc.c的copy_mm里面&#xff0c;创建新进程的时候拷贝原有进程的mm_struct&#xff0c;然后在dup_mmap前后内存加锁了</p>\n<pre>    lock_mm(oldmm);\n    {\n        ret = dup_mmap(mm, oldmm);\n    }\n    unlock_mm(oldmm);</pre>\n<p>我不太理解这样做的意义何在啊&#xff1f;</p>\n<p>dup_mmap读取原有oldmm中的内容&#xff0c;写到新的mm里面去&#xff0c;是对原有oldmm的一个只读操作&#xff0c;为什么要加锁呢&#xff1f;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>", "subject": "关于lock_mm的用处"}], "s_edits": [], "is_bookmarked": false, "tag_good_arr": [], "request_instructor_me": false, "my_favorite": false, "t": 1446636210997, "children": [{"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-05-07T07:41:15Z", "id": "i9dv7k3vrzric", "tag_endorse": [{"class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "name": "Ruidong CAO", "id": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "photo": null, "admin": true, "us": false}], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hxu22d7okof4c1", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-05-07T07:41:15Z", "content": "<p>lock_mm(oldmm)是为了防止边复制oldmm边被修改。现在看起来只有一处lock_mm&#xff0c;当然没有用&#xff0c;但到lab8里面就好多地方用lock_mm了。</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": ["hs2swpdtr91gu"], "children": [], "type": "s_answer"}, {"is_tag_endorse": false, "created": "2015-05-07T07:47:13Z", "id": "i9dvf80ff3a4la", "tag_endorse": [], "folders": [], "history": [{"uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-05-07T07:49:03Z", "content": "<p></p>", "subject": ""}, {"uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-05-07T07:48:12Z", "content": "<p></p>", "subject": ""}, {"uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "anon": "no", "created": "2015-05-07T07:47:13Z", "content": "<p>在lab8中会有更多的函数调用lock_mm&#xff0c;在这里加锁是有必要的&#xff0c;防止读取的内容被修改</p>", "subject": ""}], "config": {}, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_order": 2, "bucket_name": "Today", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "children": [], "type": "i_answer"}], "type": "question", "unique_views": 43, "created": "2015-05-07T07:17:45Z", "id": "i9dudbt5alg262", "no_answer": 0, "nr": 397, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "upvote_ids": [], "is_tag_good": false, "config": {}, "folders": ["lab7"], "bucket_order": 2, "change_log": [{"uid": "i6roqnlkmtw", "when": "2015-05-07T07:17:45Z", "data": "i9dudbt8g8j263", "anon": "no", "type": "create"}, {"uid": "hxu22d7okof4c1", "when": "2015-05-07T07:41:15Z", "data": "i9dv7k4zlvoie", "to": "i9dudbt5alg262", "anon": "no", "type": "s_answer"}, {"uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "when": "2015-05-07T07:47:13Z", "data": "i9dvf80hk764lb", "to": "i9dudbt5alg262", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "when": "2015-05-07T07:48:12Z", "data": "i9dvgheencp3x0", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer_update"}, {"uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "when": "2015-05-07T07:49:03Z", "data": "i9dvhkvbjum43i", "anon": "no", "type": "i_answer_update"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "tags": ["lab7", "student"], "no_answer_followup": 0, "num_favorites": 0, "tag_good": []}}